<subSubSection id="76FCAB001400E3BC260AF4352E1862A2" pageId="25" pageNumber="50" type="diagnostic characters">
<paragraph id="DF370DBD38E092E9668B4EA1E0A58696" pageId="25" pageNumber="50">Diagnostic characters.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="57733B07601654C68F8C23CCC2F98A33" pageId="25" pageNumber="50">
<taxonomicName id="A22D66B92336C2B3B1A829640CCE9482" class="Dicotyledoneae" family="Asteraceae" genus="Camchaya" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="" order="Campanulales" pageId="25" pageNumber="50" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="species" species="gracilis">
<emphasis id="F3F5EF51470106D3266C7E9D316F47E3" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="50">Camchaya gracilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is characterized by phyllaries without marginal spines, achenes with 4-5 ribs and leaves that are narrowly elliptic-oblong. This species is included in 
<taxonomicName id="17B824471B27CD0135B64D9E583C96EB" class="Dicotyledoneae" family="Asteraceae" genus="Camchaya" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="" order="Campanulales" pageId="25" pageNumber="50" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="2228E88CFC6B486FF173A14C5FAE8318" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="50">Camchaya</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as it shares 6-porate pollen found in no other genera.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
